# Level 5: FreeLang 구조체와 객체 ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

**목표**: 구조체와 메서드를 이용하여 객체 지향 설계를 한다.

## 📚 강의 내용

### 1. 구조체 (Struct)

```freelang
struct Person {
  name: str,
  age: i32,
  email: str
}

let person = Person {
  name: "Alice",
  age: 30,
  email: "alice@example.com"
}

println(person.name)
println(person.age)
```

### 2. 메서드

```freelang
impl Person {
  fn new(name: str, age: i32, email: str) -> Person {
    Person { name, age, email }
  }

  fn is_adult(&self) -> bool {
    self.age >= 18
  }

  fn update_age(&mut self, new_age: i32) {
    self.age = new_age
  }
}

let mut p = Person::new("Bob", 25, "bob@example.com")
println(p.is_adult())
p.update_age(26)
```

### 3. 트레이트 (Trait)

```freelang
trait Drawable {
  fn draw(&self);
  fn area(&self) -> f64;
}

struct Circle {
  radius: f64
}

impl Drawable for Circle {
  fn draw(&self) {
    println("Drawing circle")
  }

  fn area(&self) -> f64 {
    3.14159 * self.radius * self.radius
  }
}
```

### 4. 상속과 조합

```freelang
struct Animal {
  name: str,
  age: i32
}

struct Dog {
  animal: Animal,
  breed: str
}

impl Dog {
  fn make_sound(&self) {
    println("Woof!")
  }
}
```

### 5. 제네릭

```freelang
struct Container<T> {
  value: T
}

impl<T> Container<T> {
  fn get(&self) -> &T {
    &self.value
  }

  fn set(&mut self, value: T) {
    self.value = value
  }
}
```

